item.title: Popcorn Brain
item.description: 引子 I’ve got a chance to rest for a couple of weeks without working. Not engaged with too many things. Get up early and do exercise. I’ve also figured out a few things. 我的大脑成了一个“popcorn brain” My brain is overloaded. 我总是不自觉地去做很
